plt.scatter(df.Age,df.Medv, label=f'Age Correlation = {np.round(np.corrcoef(df.Age,df.Medv)[0,1], 2)}')
plt.scatter(df.Tax,df.Medv, label=f'Tax Correlation = {np.round(np.corrcoef(df.Tax,df.Medv)[0,1], 2)}')
